summaries.text:
Data scientist salaries vary significantly by industry: Technology ranges from \$100,000 to \$150,000; Finance ranges from \$120,000 to \$160,000; Healthcare ranges from \$110,000 to \$140,00$ per year; Retail ranges from \$90,0$ to \$13\text{ } 
\$$, and Government ranges from \$80,0$ to \$12\text{ } 
\$$. Technology, Finance, and Healthcare are noted as having particularly strong demand for data scientists due to their reliance on data analysis.

